  (1) **Eisenstein unit count**: `|{u : ZOmega | u.normSq = 1}| = 6`
       вҖ” six units `{1, -1, Пү, -Пү, 1+Пү, -1-Пү}` form `C_6` under
       multiplication, generated by `О¶_6 = 1 + Пү = -ПүВІ`.
  (2) **Atomicity product**: `NS В· NT = 3 В· 2 = 6`
       вҖ” bipartite split of the d=5 universe.
  (3) **d + 1 = 6**
