  (4) **Sym(3) order = 3! = 6**
       вҖ” Pauli Оө_abc non-zero entries / permutations / Lorentz
       SO(3) generators per Pauli decomposition.
  (5) **SU(NS) root count = NS В· (NS вҲ’ 1) = 6**
       вҖ” SU(3) has 6 simple roots in its root system.
  (6) **K_{m,n} bipartite SвҖ“T cross-pair count = NS В· NT = 6**
       вҖ” at base c = 1 multiplicity; c = 2 doubles to 12.
  (7) **SO(3, 1) Lorentz generator count = ((d вҲ’ 1)(d вҲ’ 2))/2 = 6**
       вҖ” 3 rotations + 3 boosts (the d = 5 ambient gives 4 spatial
