  (8) **О”вҒҙ + K_{3,2}^{(c=2)} dual filling defect**: their Euler
       characteristics sum to `вҲ’6 = вҲ’(NS В· NT)`.  Decided вҲ…-axiom
       at `dual_fillings_sum_eq_neg_eisenstein`.
  (9) **Оұ_GUT numerator**: `Оұ_GUT = 6 / (dВІ В· ПҖВІ) = 6 / (25 В· ПҖВІ)`
       вҖ” the leading rational coefficient.
  (10) **3-cell-permutation count of the residue clauses**: clause
       1 (distinguishing), clause 2 (residue-is-something), clause 3
       (symmetric pairing) вҖ” three structural clauses, 3! = 6
