fewer) вҖ” was the remaining piece

This closure was completed via the diophantine bound chain:
  В· `four_normSq_ring_identity` (`Meta/Int213/Bound.lean В§3`):
      `(2a вҲ’ b)ВІ + 3В·bВІ = 4В·(aВІ вҲ’ ab + bВІ)` (Int ring algebra)
  В· `int_sq_nonneg`, `three_sq_le_four_implies`,
    `le_of_add_eq_of_nonneg` (`Meta/Int213/Bound.lean В§4`):
